         <abstract id="aspace_811ee6ea6a67d6bb2928532ec5b0608d">Miscellaneous autographs and letters of American political and cultural figures, among them John and John Quincy Adams, Daniel Webster, Jefferson Davis, Horace Greeley, and Lydia Sigourney. Also included are eleven letters to James F. Babcock, editor of the <title render="italic">
               <part>New Haven Weekly Palladium</part>
            </title>, on politics (1840-1866) and seven letters (1866-1872) to R. P. Cowles in New Haven from prospective lecturers.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname relator="col" source="local">
